data.description: This is presently an adult foster care facility and may be purchased as a residential home for the listed asking price. If you want to purchase the business and state licenses as well the price would be $700,000 total. The home is expansive with the upstairs being used as an owner's living suite. The roof was replaced in 2014 and there have been numerous other upgrades including windows and flooring. Out back is a wonderful inground pool that is secured by fencing. This home would also work well to rent bedrooms out separately as an income producing property.  Located in a great East Medford neighbor this home is close to shopping, schools and medical and is ready to serve your needs.
